489
00:19:19,237 --> 00:19:21,737
kurts tsu di zakh, vos hot, vos hot pasirt?

490
00:19:21,737 --> 00:19:23,957
pasirt hot, farshteystu, az di khevre

491
00:19:23,957 --> 00:19:26,787
hobn geshoybn. veyst ⟨vos taytsh⟩ geshoybn?

492
