590
00:23:49,267 --> 00:23:51,437
zey zenen shoyn dort gevezn

591
00:23:51,437 --> 00:23:52,649
in dem lager.

592
00:23:52,649 --> 00:23:54,689
azoy zenen mir dort gevezn, farshteystu

593
00:23:54,689 --> 00:23:55,939
