650
00:26:00,794 --> 00:26:03,727
fun Lodzh gevezn dort. kh'hob getrofn mayns a kuzin

651
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:06,057
fun dem

652
00:26:06,057 --> 00:26:09,096
un dort mit mir, ikh bin ge- mitge⟨UNK⟩ shoyn gevorn a

653
00:26:09,096 --> 00:26:10,116
a goen

654
00:26:10,116 --> 00:26:12,076
vayl ikh bin nokh gekumen mit di kapos.

655
00:26:10,803 --> 00:26:13,693
dos iz shoyn onfang finef un fertsikstn

656
00:26:13,613 --> 00:26:14,463
JA, JA.

657
00:26:13,693 --> 00:26:16,580
haltn mir shoyn, yo? vinter finef un fertsik.

658
00:26:16,343 --> 00:26:18,442
