696
00:27:30,876 --> 00:27:32,490
rays im aroys dem tson."

697
00:27:33,036 --> 00:27:34,687
iz der zun tsugegangen

698
00:27:34,687 --> 00:27:35,867
der zun, er iz do do

699
00:27:35,867 --> 00:27:37,187
a bilyarder

700
00:27:37,187 --> 00:27:38,787
hot aroysgerisn di tson

701
00:27:38,787 --> 00:27:41,867
un gegebn dem WALTER un hot im gegebn a por zupn

702
00:27:41,867 --> 00:27:42,630
azoy UNK

703
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:45,860
hot men dort geshrign vayter "vu, ver iz di fakhmener?"

704
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:52,518
ot der kapo, UNK gevolt geyn, g- vu dort vu s'iz gut, hot men gevust hot men gezogt UNK "er iz a elektriker, der iz a dos"

705
00:27:52,518 --> 00:27:53,348
der tsveyter

706
00:27:53,348 --> 00:27:55,318
hot men undz geshikt avek fun dort

707
00:27:55,318 --> 00:27:56,998
