708
00:27:56,998 --> 00:27:59,754
DORA iz gevezn, m'hot geboyt VAU eyns

709
00:27:59,754 --> 00:28:00,891
VAU tsvey

710
00:28:01,335 --> 00:28:03,220
zenen mir gekumen keyn DORA

711
00:28:03,220 --> 00:28:05,920
DORA iz geven a s- groyser lager, oykh a toyte lager.

712
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,609
m'hot gearbet ineveynik

713
00:28:07,609 --> 00:28:09,819
un di vos zey hobn gearbet in droysn bay di berg

714
00:28:09,819 --> 00:28:12,039
UNK gearbet in tuneln

715
00:28:12,039 --> 00:28:13,462
geven a toyter.

716
00:28:13,587 --> 00:28:15,794
vos hot pasirt? ikh g- dem

717
00:28:15,794 --> 00:28:16,908
⟨ZAWACKI⟩

718
00:28:16,908 --> 00:28:18,622
vos ikh hob dir dertseylt vos iz gevezn

719
00:28:18,622 --> 00:28:20,062
in

720
00:28:20,062 --> 00:28:21,022
BRESLAU

721
00:28:21,113 --> 00:28:22,339
GORLITZ

722
00:28:22,868 --> 00:28:26,345
der gantser UNK der UNK ⟨ZAWACKI⟩, der shrayber fun

723
00:28:26,345 --> 00:28:29,435
fun UNK fun VAU eyns, VAU tsvey in DORA

724
00:28:29,955 --> 00:28:32,239
bin arayngekumen ⟨tsu geyn⟩, hot men undz gegebn a numer

725
00:28:32,239 --> 00:28:34,249
ikh hob gekrign UNK mir gegebn a numer.

726
00:28:34,249 --> 00:28:36,219
host gekrign a numer fun di GORLITZ?

727
00:28:36,219 --> 00:28:37,686
ikh hob a numer fun GORLITZ.

728
00:28:37,686 --> 00:28:39,946
fun, vi heyst er, fun DORA.

729
00:28:39,946 --> 00:28:41,876
hob ikh gekrign dem numer fun DORA

730
00:28:41,876 --> 00:28:43,674
un er hot undz dort getrofn

731
00:28:43,674 --> 00:28:46,024
un m'hot dort geganen. ikh ⟨hob⟩ gevorn

732
00:28:46,024 --> 00:28:48,104
der forman.

733
00:28:48,906 --> 00:28:50,129
dort bin ikh gevorn

734
00:28:50,129 --> 00:28:51,099
der forman

735
00:28:51,099 --> 00:28:52,369
UNK fun ts-

736
00:28:52,369 --> 00:28:54,299
tsu boyen dem tramv- tsu UNK

737
00:28:54,299 --> 00:28:54,929
di

738
00:28:54,929 --> 00:28:57,164
aparatn vos geyt aroyf tsum

739
00:28:57,164 --> 00:28:59,454
tsu flign tsu nokh LONDON, tsu bombn LONDON

740
00:28:59,454 --> 00:29:00,514
on a mentshn.

741
00:29:00,514 --> 00:29:01,803
bin ikh dort gevorn.

742
00:29:01,803 --> 00:29:03,513
nor dort bin ikh gevezn.

743
00:29:03,705 --> 00:29:06,714
un dort bin ikh geshlofn in, in, a pritshe

744
00:29:06,714 --> 00:29:08,524
vos iz gelign a rus

745
00:29:08,524 --> 00:29:10,574
un ikh hob gekrign a gut hemd

746
00:29:10,574 --> 00:29:14,184
un ikh heyb mikh oy- er iz gel- ikh bin gelign azoy, un er iz gelign azoy.

747
00:29:14,184 --> 00:29:15,680
mayn hemd iz nishto.

748
00:29:16,615 --> 00:29:20,709
hot tsugenumen dos hemd, hot er mir avekgevorfn a farloyzt hemd. s'iz geven geferlekh LAUS.

749
00:29:21,458 --> 00:29:25,671
hob ikh nisht gevolt ontun dos hemd un aropgeyn tsu UNK. iz geganen der kapo dort fun dem tsimer

750
00:29:25,963 --> 00:29:27,983
un er hot mir es ge- UNK ⟨gegebn⟩

751
00:29:27,983 --> 00:29:29,803
tsvontsik oyfn ⟨ARSCH⟩

752
00:29:29,803 --> 00:29:32,043
hot mir aropgenumen kop arayn azoy

753
00:29:32,043 --> 00:29:33,973
un geshtanen, un er hot mir gegebn mit a shpadl

754
00:29:33,973 --> 00:29:35,313
hot mir gegebn dem ershtn

755
00:29:35,313 --> 00:29:36,919
bin ikh shoyn nisht gevezn keyn mentsh.

756
00:29:36,919 --> 00:29:38,509
shoyn nisht ge- veys nisht vifl ikh hob gekrign.

757
00:29:38,509 --> 00:29:39,542
ikh bin gelign.

758
00:29:39,852 --> 00:29:41,831
UNK eyn molt kumt a selektsye

759
00:29:41,831 --> 00:29:43,421
arayn in lager arayn

760
00:29:43,421 --> 00:29:46,211
a selektsye UNK selektsye. ver geyt mit mit di selektsye?

761
00:29:46,211 --> 00:29:47,351
der ⟨ZAWACKI⟩.

762
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:51,877
"vos tustu do?" hob ikh im dertseylt

763
00:29:53,402 --> 00:29:54,630
hob ikh im dertseylt

764
00:29:54,630 --> 00:29:55,910
vos do tut zikh.

765
00:29:56,068 --> 00:29:58,658
⟨iz⟩ geganen, hot er mikh arayngenumen tsu zayn shtub arayn

766
00:29:58,658 --> 00:30:01,448
un dort bin ikh gelign a por tog, un ikh hob mikh oysgeheylt.

767
00:30:02,211 --> 00:30:02,992
shoyn.

768
00:30:02,992 --> 00:30:04,685
un gey vayter oyf mayn arbet.

769
00:30:04,708 --> 00:30:07,798
